<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Bottleneck Scan | VYRTŪOSITI</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Raw proof from VYRTŪOSITI and a private diagnostic for identifying the hidden bottleneck costing clarity, energy, execution, or leverage." />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#050505" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Playfair+Display:wght@500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #050505;
      --panel: #0D0D0B;
      --panel-2: #11110E;
      --gold: #B8965A;
      --gold-soft: #D7C08A;
      --text: #F4F0E8;
      --muted: #A9A39A;
      --quiet: #746F66;
      --border: rgba(184,150,90,.22);
      --border-soft: rgba(184,150,90,.13);
      --max: 1160px;
      --radius: 22px;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      width: 100%;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
      background: var(--bg);
    }

    body {
      width: 100%;
      min-width: 0;
      margin: 0;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(184,150,90,.10), transparent 34rem),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #050505 0%, #060605 58%, #030303 100%);
      line-height: 1.55;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
    }

    img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: var(--max);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 28px;
    }

    .nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 50;
      background: rgba(5,5,5,.84);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    }

    .nav-inner {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1280px;
      min-height: 74px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 28px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      min-width: 0;
      letter-spacing: .13em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: .84rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .brand-mark {
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      flex: 0 0 34px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      font-family: "Playfair Display", Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 24px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .82rem;
      letter-spacing: .04em;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 46px;
      padding: 0 22px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(184,150,90,.04);
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      font-size: .74rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .13em;
      transition: border-color .2s ease, background .2s ease;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      border-color: rgba(215,192,138,.58);
      background: rgba(184,150,90,.10);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 112px 0 76px;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(340px, .72fr);
      gap: 56px;
      align-items: end;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .18em;
      font-size: .72rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .eyebrow::before {
      content: "";
      width: 44px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--gold);
      opacity: .78;
    }

    h1, h2, h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Playfair Display", Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -.045em;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    h1 {
      max-width: 820px;
      font-size: clamp(4.1rem, 7.8vw, 8.5rem);
      line-height: .95;
    }

    h2 {
      max-width: 780px;
      font-size: clamp(2.7rem, 5.1vw, 5.2rem);
      line-height: .98;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 32px 0 0;
      color: rgba(244,240,232,.76);
      font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.4vw, 1.24rem);
      line-height: 1.72;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 34px;
    }

    .secondary-link {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .86rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(169,163,154,.36);
      padding-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .metric-card,
    .card,
    .quote-card,
    .case-card,
    .archive,
    .final-card,
    .bridge,
    .source-card,
    .outcome-card,
    .inline-cta {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.035), transparent 50%),
        var(--panel);
    }

    .metric-card {
      padding: 36px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 0%, rgba(184,150,90,.14), transparent 42%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.04), transparent 56%),
        var(--panel);
    }

    .label {
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .16em;
      font-size: .68rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .claim-note {
      margin-top: 28px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .16em;
      font-size: .68rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .metric-number {
      margin: 8px 0 24px;
      font-family: "Playfair Display", Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem);
      line-height: .85;
      letter-spacing: -.06em;
    }

    .quote {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(244,240,232,.84);
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .byline {
      margin-top: 22px;
      padding-top: 18px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: .88rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .role {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 5px;
      color: var(--quiet);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .13em;
      font-size: .68rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .stars {
      margin-top: 8px;
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      font-size: .78rem;
    }

    .cred-strip,
    .proof-strip {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1px;
      margin-top: 34px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: var(--border-soft);
    }

    .proof-strip {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    }

    .cred-item,
    .proof-point {
      padding: 22px;
      background: rgba(13,13,11,.88);
    }

    .cred-item strong,
    .proof-point strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .14em;
      font-size: .68rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .cred-item span,
    .proof-point span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .88rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    section {
      padding: 92px 0;
    }

    .section-tight {
      padding: 72px 0;
    }

    .section-head {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, .9fr) minmax(300px, .58fr);
      gap: 56px;
      align-items: end;
      margin-bottom: 38px;
    }

    .section-copy {
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .quote-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .quote-card {
      min-width: 0;
      min-height: 310px;
      padding: 30px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .quote-card.featured {
      min-height: 385px;
      padding: 36px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 84% 0%, rgba(184,150,90,.12), transparent 38%),
        var(--panel-2);
    }

    .quote-text {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(244,240,232,.86);
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.68;
    }

    .quote-card.featured .quote-text,
    .source-card .big-quote {
      font-family: "Playfair Display", Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.45rem, 2.05vw, 2.1rem);
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -.025em;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .proof-stack {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, .92fr) minmax(340px, .68fr);
      gap: 22px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .source-card {
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .source-copy {
      padding: 36px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    }

    .proof-note {
      margin: 16px 0 0;
      color: var(--quiet);
      font-size: .78rem;
    }

    .source-image-wrap {
      padding: 12px;
      background: #F4F0E8;
    }

    .source-image {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 14px;
    }

    .outcome-stack {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .outcome-card {
      padding: 32px;
      min-height: 250px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .outcome-title {
      margin: 12px 0 22px;
      font-family: "Playfair Display", Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4.2vw, 4.2rem);
      line-height: .92;
      letter-spacing: -.055em;
    }

    .pattern-block {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      background: rgba(184,150,90,.025);
    }

    .pattern-inner {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, .86fr) minmax(320px, .68fr);
      gap: 56px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .pattern-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .pattern-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 104px 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      padding: 18px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    }

    .pattern-item strong {
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .13em;
      font-size: .68rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .pattern-item span {
      color: rgba(244,240,232,.82);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .bridge {
      padding: 42px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(184,150,90,.10), transparent 48%),
        var(--panel);
    }

    .bridge-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1px;
      margin-top: 32px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 18px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--border-soft);
    }

    .bridge-item {
      padding: 26px;
      background: rgba(13,13,11,.9);
    }

    .bridge-item strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .13em;
      font-size: .66rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .bridge-item p {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(244,240,232,.82);
      font-size: .94rem;
      line-height: 1.62;
    }

    .partnership-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .case-card {
      min-width: 0;
      padding: 30px;
    }

    .case-card.flagship {
      border-color: rgba(215,192,138,.35);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 82% 0%, rgba(184,150,90,.13), transparent 40%),
        var(--panel);
    }

    .case-topline {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      padding-bottom: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    }

    .case-name {
      font-family: "Playfair Display", Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 2rem;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -.04em;
    }

    .case-type {
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .13em;
      font-size: .66rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .case-matrix {
      display: grid;
      gap: 11px;
    }

    .case-row {
      padding: 15px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.018);
    }

    .case-row strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .13em;
      font-size: .62rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .case-row span {
      display: block;
      color: rgba(244,240,232,.82);
      font-size: .9rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .case-signal {
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .case-proof-line {
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .11em;
      font-size: .72rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.45;
    }

    .case-disclaimer {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 26px 0 0;
      color: var(--quiet);
      font-size: .78rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .inline-cta {
      margin-top: 34px;
      padding: 28px 30px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .inline-cta p {
      max-width: 740px;
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(244,240,232,.82);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .archive {
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .archive-head {
      padding: 28px 30px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .archive-head h3 {
      font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif;
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .16em;
      font-size: .72rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .archive-note {
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 8px 0 0;
      color: var(--quiet);
      font-size: .82rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .archive-count {
      color: var(--quiet);
      font-size: .82rem;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .archive-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .mini-quote {
      padding: 24px 28px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    }

    .mini-quote:nth-child(even) {
      border-right: 0;
    }

    .mini-quote p {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      color: rgba(244,240,232,.78);
      font-size: .92rem;
      line-height: 1.62;
    }

    .mini-quote .mini-name {
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: .78rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .closing {
      padding: 112px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .closing .container {
      max-width: 920px;
    }

    .closing h2 {
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .closing p {
      max-width: 660px;
      margin: 28px auto 0;
      color: rgba(244,240,232,.78);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.76;
    }

    .final-card {
      margin-top: 42px;
      padding: 40px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(184,150,90,.13), transparent 48%),
        var(--panel);
    }

    .footer {
      padding: 40px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      color: var(--quiet);
      font-size: .82rem;
    }

    .footer-inner {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .footer strong {
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .14em;
      font-size: .78rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero {
        padding: 82px 0 52px;
      }

      .hero-grid,
      .section-head,
      .proof-stack,
      .pattern-inner,
      .partnership-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .quote-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .proof-strip {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }

      .cred-strip,
      .bridge-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .quote-card,
      .quote-card.featured {
        min-height: auto;
      }

      .source-card {
        order: 2;
      }

      .outcome-stack {
        order: 1;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .container,
      .nav-inner {
        padding-left: 18px;
        padding-right: 18px;
      }

      .nav-inner {
        min-height: 66px;
      }

      .brand span:last-child {
        display: none;
      }

      .nav-links a:not(.btn) {
        display: none;
      }

      .nav .btn {
        min-height: 42px;
        padding: 0 14px;
        font-size: .66rem;
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 62px 0 42px;
      }

      .eyebrow {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-size: .66rem;
      }

      .eyebrow::before {
        width: 34px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(3.0rem, 15vw, 4.2rem);
        line-height: .96;
        letter-spacing: -.04em;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 10.5vw, 3.35rem);
        line-height: 1;
      }

      .hero-copy {
        margin-top: 22px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.62;
      }

      .hero-actions {
        align-items: stretch;
        flex-direction: column;
        margin-top: 26px;
      }

      .hero-actions .btn,
      .hero-actions .secondary-link {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .secondary-link {
        border-bottom: 0;
      }

      .cred-strip,
      .proof-strip {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        margin-top: 26px;
      }

      .metric-card,
      .quote-card,
      .quote-card.featured,
      .outcome-card,
      .case-card,
      .bridge,
      .final-card {
        padding: 24px;
        border-radius: 18px;
      }

      .metric-number,
      .outcome-title {
        font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 15vw, 4.2rem);
      }

      section,
      .section-tight {
        padding: 62px 0;
      }

      .section-head {
        margin-bottom: 28px;
        gap: 24px;
      }

      .source-copy {
        padding: 24px;
      }

      .source-card .big-quote {
        font-size: clamp(1.45rem, 7vw, 2.1rem);
      }

      .bridge-grid {
        margin-top: 24px;
      }

      .bridge-item {
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .case-topline {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .case-type {
        text-align: left;
      }

      .case-name {
        font-size: 1.85rem;
      }

      .inline-cta {
        padding: 24px;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: stretch;
      }

      .inline-cta .btn {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .archive-head {
        padding: 24px;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .archive-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .mini-quote,
      .mini-quote:nth-child(even) {
        border-right: 0;
      }

      .closing {
        padding: 78px 0;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 420px) {
      .container,
      .nav-inner {
        padding-left: 16px;
        padding-right: 16px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 14vw, 3.45rem);
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: clamp(2.0rem, 10vw, 2.85rem);
      }
    }
  
    /* ---- v14 UX edge refinement: stable, conservative, accessible ---- */
    :focus-visible {
      outline: 2px solid var(--gold-soft);
      outline-offset: 4px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    section {
      scroll-margin-top: 96px;
    }

    .skip-link {
      position: absolute;
      left: 16px;
      top: -100px;
      z-index: 999;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      background: var(--gold-soft);
      color: #050505;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: .8rem;
      transition: top .2s ease;
    }

    .skip-link:focus {
      top: 16px;
    }

    .hero-proof-note {
      margin-top: 18px;
      color: var(--quiet);
      font-size: .78rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .section-subnote {
      margin-top: 18px;
      color: var(--quiet);
      font-size: .82rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 620px;
    }

    .btn-row-tight {
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .micro-divider {
      height: 1px;
      width: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(184,150,90,.25), transparent);
      margin: 18px 0 0;
    }

    .case-proof-line {
      padding-top: 18px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    }

    .final-card .btn {
      min-width: 230px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      section {
        scroll-margin-top: 78px;
      }

      .skip-link {
        display: none;
      }

      .hero-proof-note,
      .section-subnote {
        font-size: .76rem;
      }

      .final-card .btn {
        min-width: 0;
        width: 100%;
      }
    }

  
    /* ---- v15 label refinement ---- */
    .mini-name {
      line-height: 1.45;
    }

    .role {
      line-height: 1.45;
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .mini-name {
        font-size: .76rem;
      }
    }

  
    /* ---- v16 spacing, sequencing, and formatting refinement ---- */
    :root {
      --max: 1120px;
    }

    .container {
      padding-left: 30px;
      padding-right: 30px;
    }

    .hero {
      padding-top: 104px;
      padding-bottom: 66px;
    }

    .hero-copy-secondary {
      margin-top: 14px;
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      font-size: .98rem;
      letter-spacing: .01em;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .cred-strip,
    .proof-strip {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    section {
      padding-top: 84px;
      padding-bottom: 84px;
    }

    .section-tight {
      padding-top: 68px;
      padding-bottom: 68px;
    }

    .section-head {
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      gap: 44px;
    }

    .quote-grid,
    .partnership-grid {
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .quote-card {
      padding: 28px;
      min-height: 286px;
    }

    .quote-card.featured {
      padding: 34px;
      min-height: 350px;
    }

    .proof-stack {
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .outcome-stack {
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .metric-card,
    .bridge,
    .final-card {
      box-shadow: 0 26px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.32);
    }

    .metric-card {
      padding: 34px;
    }

    .source-copy {
      padding: 34px;
    }

    .outcome-card {
      padding: 30px;
    }

    .bridge {
      padding: 38px;
    }

    .bridge-grid {
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .case-card {
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .case-topline {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      padding-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .case-row {
      padding: 14px;
    }

    .inline-cta {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 26px 28px;
    }

    .pattern-block {
      padding-top: 72px;
      padding-bottom: 72px;
    }

    .pattern-item {
      padding: 16px 0;
    }

    .archive-head {
      padding-top: 26px;
      padding-bottom: 26px;
    }

    .mini-quote {
      padding-top: 22px;
      padding-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .closing {
      padding-top: 96px;
      padding-bottom: 96px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero {
        padding-top: 78px;
        padding-bottom: 50px;
      }

      section,
      .section-tight {
        padding-top: 60px;
        padding-bottom: 60px;
      }

      .pattern-block {
        padding-top: 58px;
        padding-bottom: 58px;
      }

      .section-head {
        gap: 22px;
        margin-bottom: 26px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .container,
      .nav-inner {
        padding-left: 18px;
        padding-right: 18px;
      }

      .hero {
        padding-top: 54px;
        padding-bottom: 36px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.85rem, 14vw, 3.85rem);
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: clamp(2.05rem, 9.6vw, 3.05rem);
      }

      .hero-copy {
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .hero-copy-secondary {
        margin-top: 10px;
        font-size: .92rem;
      }

      .metric-card,
      .quote-card,
      .quote-card.featured,
      .outcome-card,
      .case-card,
      .bridge,
      .final-card {
        padding: 22px;
      }

      .cred-item,
      .proof-point,
      .bridge-item {
        padding: 18px;
      }

      .source-copy,
      .archive-head,
      .mini-quote {
        padding-left: 22px;
        padding-right: 22px;
      }

      .inline-cta {
        padding: 22px;
      }

      .closing {
        padding-top: 70px;
        padding-bottom: 70px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 420px) {
      .container,
      .nav-inner {
        padding-left: 16px;
        padding-right: 16px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.62rem, 13.2vw, 3.2rem);
      }

      .metric-number,
      .outcome-title {
        font-size: clamp(2.95rem, 14vw, 3.85rem);
      }
    }

  
    /* ---- v17 conversion hardening ---- */
    .scan-process-grid,
    .fit-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .scan-step,
    .fit-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.035), transparent 52%),
        var(--panel);
      padding: 28px;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .scan-step-number {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      font-size: .72rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      background: rgba(184,150,90,.06);
    }

    .scan-step h3,
    .fit-card h3 {
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;
      font-size: .78rem;
      line-height: 1.25;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .14em;
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      font-weight: 900;
      margin: 0 0 14px;
    }

    .scan-step p,
    .fit-card p {
      color: rgba(244,240,232,.82);
      font-size: .94rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .scan-microcopy {
      margin-top: 24px;
      color: var(--quiet);
      font-size: .82rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .fit-card ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: rgba(244,240,232,.82);
      font-size: .93rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .fit-card li + li {
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .fit-card.negative {
      border-color: rgba(184,150,90,.12);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.015);
    }

    .cta-microcopy {
      margin-top: 14px;
      color: var(--quiet);
      font-size: .8rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .final-card .cta-microcopy {
      max-width: 520px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .scan-process-grid,
      .fit-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .scan-step,
      .fit-card {
        padding: 22px;
      }

      .scan-step-number {
        margin-bottom: 18px;
      }
    }

  
    /* ---- v18 hero proof rebalance ---- */
    .hero-scan-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
      margin: 28px 0 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .hero-scan-list li {
      padding: 16px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      color: rgba(244,240,232,.84);
      font-size: .96rem;
      line-height: 1.62;
    }

    .hero-scan-list li:first-child {
      border-top: 0;
      padding-top: 0;
    }

    .hero-scan-list strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .13em;
      font-size: .64rem;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .hero-scan-note {
      margin-top: 24px;
      padding-top: 18px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      color: var(--quiet);
      font-size: .8rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .supporting-proof {
      border-color: rgba(184,150,90,.18);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.025), transparent 54%),
        var(--panel);
    }

    .supporting-proof .outcome-title {
      font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 4.8vw, 4.7rem);
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .hero-scan-list {
        margin-top: 22px;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .hero-scan-list li {
        padding: 14px 0;
        font-size: .92rem;
      }
    }

  
    /* ---- v19 above-the-fold optimization ---- */
    @media (min-width: 981px) {
      .hero {
        padding-top: 64px;
        padding-bottom: 46px;
      }

      .hero-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, .98fr) minmax(360px, .72fr);
        gap: 46px;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .eyebrow {
        margin-bottom: 22px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(4.2rem, 6.2vw, 6.75rem);
        line-height: .94;
        max-width: 780px;
      }

      .hero-copy {
        margin-top: 24px;
        max-width: 620px;
        font-size: 1.08rem;
        line-height: 1.66;
      }

      .hero-copy-secondary {
        margin-top: 10px;
      }

      .hero-actions {
        margin-top: 26px;
      }

      .metric-card {
        align-self: center;
        padding: 30px;
        max-width: 430px;
        margin-left: auto;
      }

      .hero-scan-list {
        margin-top: 22px;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .hero-scan-list li {
        padding: 13px 0;
        font-size: .92rem;
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .hero-scan-note {
        margin-top: 18px;
        padding-top: 16px;
      }

      .proof-strip {
        margin-top: 26px;
      }

      .proof-point {
        padding: 18px 20px;
      }
    }

    @media (min-width: 1280px) {
      .hero {
        min-height: calc(100vh - 74px);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        padding-top: 46px;
        padding-bottom: 42px;
      }

      .hero .container:first-child {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .proof-strip {
        margin-top: 24px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero {
        padding-top: 56px;
        padding-bottom: 38px;
      }

      .metric-card {
        margin-top: 4px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .hero {
        padding-top: 44px;
        padding-bottom: 32px;
      }

      .eyebrow {
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      .hero-copy {
        margin-top: 18px;
      }

      .hero-actions {
        margin-top: 22px;
      }

      .metric-card {
        margin-top: 8px;
      }

      .proof-strip {
        margin-top: 22px;
      }
    }

  
    /* ---- v20 Ted Tanner public review addition ---- */
    .quote-card.public-source {
      border-color: rgba(215,192,138,.30);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 82% 0%, rgba(184,150,90,.10), transparent 42%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.03), transparent 52%),
        var(--panel);
    }

    .source-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 12px;
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      font-size: .72rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .12em;
      font-weight: 800;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(215,192,138,.28);
      padding-bottom: 3px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 981px) {
      .quote-grid.four-up {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      }

      .quote-grid.four-up .quote-card {
        min-height: 330px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 1180px) and (min-width: 981px) {
      .quote-grid.four-up {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
    }

  
    /* ---- v21 proof consolidation polish ---- */
    @media (min-width: 981px) {
      #proof .quote-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      }

      #proof .quote-card.featured {
        min-height: 430px;
      }

      #recent-partnerships .partnership-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      }

      #recent-partnerships .case-card {
        padding: 24px;
      }

      #recent-partnerships .case-name {
        font-size: 1.72rem;
      }

      #recent-partnerships .case-row span {
        font-size: .86rem;
      }
    }

    .quote-card .label {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .source-card .big-quote {
      font-size: clamp(1.28rem, 1.7vw, 1.76rem);
    }

    .archive {
      opacity: .94;
    }

    .archive-note {
      max-width: 640px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      #proof .quote-card.featured {
        min-height: auto;
      }
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <a class="skip-link" href="#main">Skip to content</a>
  <header class="nav">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a class="brand" href="#">
        <span class="brand-mark">V</span>
        <span>VYRTŪOSITI</span>
      </a>
      <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="Primary navigation">
        <a href="#proof">Proof</a>
        <a href="#scan-logic">Logic</a>
        <a href="#recent-partnerships">Cases</a>
        <a class="btn" href="https://www.marcuslefton.com/bottleneck">Scan</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="main">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Raw proof</div>
          <h1>The work is private.<br>The results are not.</h1>
          <p class="hero-copy">Private performance advisory for founders, executives, athletes, and high-performing operators carrying constraints that cost time, energy, focus, money, or momentum.</p>
          <p class="hero-copy hero-copy-secondary">Proof that the right diagnosis changes the next move.</p>

          <div class="cred-strip" aria-label="Credibility context">
            <div class="cred-item"><strong>15+ years</strong><span>Applied performance across pro sport, executive performance, private advisory, and flow science.</span></div>
            <div class="cred-item"><strong>High stakes</strong><span>From MLB systems and elite athletes to founders, operators, and executive clients.</span></div>
            <div class="cred-item"><strong>Diagnosis first</strong><span>The work starts by finding the constraint actually costing clarity, energy, or execution.</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn" href="https://www.marcuslefton.com/bottleneck">Start Bottleneck Scan</a>
            <a class="secondary-link" href="#scan-process">What happens inside</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="metric-card">
          <div class="label">Private diagnostic</div>
          <div class="claim-note">What the Scan clarifies</div>
          <ul class="hero-scan-list">
            <li><strong>Visible problem</strong>The symptom you can already name.</li>
            <li><strong>Real constraint</strong>The hidden layer creating the drag.</li>
            <li><strong>Next move</strong>What to stop, what to change, and where to focus first.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="hero-scan-note">For serious operators who need sharper diagnosis, not generic productivity advice.</p>
        </aside>
      </div>

      <div class="container">
        <div class="proof-strip">
          <div class="proof-point"><strong>Clarity</strong><span>Seeing the real constraint.</span></div>
          <div class="proof-point"><strong>Calm</strong><span>Staying steady inside complexity.</span></div>
          <div class="proof-point"><strong>Action</strong><span>Leaving with practical next steps.</span></div>
          <div class="proof-point"><strong>Trust</strong><span>Being deeply heard and accurately challenged.</span></div>
          <div class="proof-point"><strong>Repeatability</strong><span>Building a better way to operate.</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="scan-logic" class="section-tight">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="bridge">
          <div class="label">Why the Bottleneck Scan exists</div>
          <h2>Most high performers are solving the wrong layer.</h2>
          <p class="section-copy" style="margin-top: 26px; max-width: 720px;">Most clients arrive with a symptom. The Scan separates what is visible from what is actually driving the cost — then clarifies the highest-leverage next move.</p>

          <div class="bridge-grid">
            <div class="bridge-item"><strong>1. Visible problem</strong><p>The symptom you can already name: stalled growth, scattered focus, low energy, unclear priorities, pressure, or inconsistent execution.</p></div>
            <div class="bridge-item"><strong>2. Hidden constraint</strong><p>The upstream mechanism creating the symptom and quietly taxing output.</p></div>
            <div class="bridge-item"><strong>3. Next move</strong><p>What to stop, what to change, and where to focus first.</p></div>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-actions btn-row-tight">
            <a class="btn" href="https://www.marcuslefton.com/bottleneck">Start Bottleneck Scan</a>
            <a class="secondary-link" href="#scan-process">What happens inside</a>
          </div>
          <p class="cta-microcopy">Private diagnostic. Built for serious operators. No generic productivity advice.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    

    <section id="scan-process" class="section-tight">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <div class="label">Inside the Scan</div>
            <h2>What happens inside the Bottleneck Scan.</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="section-copy">The Scan is designed to reduce ambiguity fast. You do not need another motivational call. You need a sharper read on the constraint beneath the symptom.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="scan-process-grid">
          <article class="scan-step">
            <div class="scan-step-number">01</div>
            <h3>Name the visible problem</h3>
            <p>The symptom you already feel: scattered focus, stalled growth, low energy, pressure, inconsistent execution, unclear priorities, or a system that no longer fits the stakes.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="scan-step">
            <div class="scan-step-number">02</div>
            <h3>Identify the real constraint</h3>
            <p>The deeper mechanism creating the drag: role collapse, recovery debt, attention fragmentation, unclear leverage, decision fatigue, weak feedback loops, or poor value capture.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="scan-step">
            <div class="scan-step-number">03</div>
            <h3>Leave with the next move</h3>
            <p>A clearer view of what to stop, what to change, and where to focus first so the next step is obvious instead of abstract.</p>
          </article>
        </div>

        <p class="scan-microcopy">This is a diagnostic, not a generic coaching call. The goal is to find the expensive constraint your current system is hiding.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

<section id="proof" class="section-tight">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <div class="label">Proof by objection</div>
            <h2>The few proof points that matter most.</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="section-copy">Each proof point below answers a different premium-buyer objection: is this worth it, does it create outcomes, and can Marcus diagnose across the real system?</p>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-grid">
          <article class="quote-card featured">
            <div>
              <div class="label">Premium value</div>
              <p class="quote-text">“The strongest testimonial I can give you is the five digit sum I pay to have six months of private advisory calls with Marcus. I feel like I am getting every penny’s worth.”</p>
            </div>
            <div class="byline">Ethan Evans<span class="role">Retired Amazon VP / premium willingness-to-pay proof</span></div>
          </article>

          <article class="quote-card featured">
            <div>
              <div class="label">Measured outcome</div>
              <p class="quote-text">“Within three months, I had my best Q1 ever, hitting almost 200% of plan — the highest I’ve performed in five years.”</p>
            </div>
            <div class="byline">David V.<span class="role">Sales performance outcome</span></div>
          </article>

          <article class="quote-card featured">
            <div>
              <div class="label">Diagnostic depth</div>
              <p class="quote-text">“He could go vertically deep and horizontally in recommending operationally, physically, and psychologically.”</p>
            </div>
            <div class="byline">Ted Tanner<span class="role">Software / technical operator · public review</span><a class="source-link" href="https://www.tedtanner.org/review-flow-research-collective/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Public source</a></div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-tight">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <div class="label">Supporting proof</div>
            <h2>Public proof without making the page a proof dump.</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="section-copy">The strongest proof is already above. This section keeps the public evidence visible without making every testimonial compete for attention.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="proof-stack">
          <article class="source-card">
            <div class="source-copy">
              <p class="big-quote">Public source proof for the premium-value claim above.</p>
              <div class="byline">Ethan Evans<span class="role">Retired Amazon VP / LinkedIn Top Voice</span></div>
              <p class="proof-note">Screenshot retained for source credibility, not to add more volume.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="source-image-wrap">
              <img class="source-image" src="data:image/webp;base64," width="900" height="840" alt="Ethan Evans LinkedIn testimonial screenshot" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
            </div>
          </article>

          <div class="outcome-stack">

            <article class="outcome-card supporting-proof">
              <div>
                <div class="label">Supporting outcome</div>
                <div class="outcome-title">$600M+ requested</div>
                <p class="quote">“Working with Marcus has resulted in two counties asking for our organization to do over $600 million of work.”</p>
              </div>
              <div class="byline">Daniel B.<span class="role">Organization leader / client-reported outcome</span></div>
            </article>

            <article class="outcome-card">
              <div>
                <div class="label">Repeated signal</div>
                <div class="outcome-title">Real stakes.</div>
                <p class="quote">Across the strongest proof, clients describe clearer decisions, stronger execution, better recovery, higher leverage, and outcomes tied to work that actually matters.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="byline">VYRTŪOSITI pattern<span class="role">Diagnosis → system → execution</span></div>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="recent-partnerships" class="section-tight">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <div class="label">Recent partnership proof</div>
            <h2>Three recent bottleneck patterns.</h2>
          </div>
